import { Flex, Heading } from "@chakra-ui/layout"

export const PlanReview=()=>{
    return(
        <>
        
        <Flex flexDirection="column" justifyContent="center" alignItems="center">
                <Flex width="md" boxShadow="lg" borderRadius="lg" P>
                    <Heading size="xl">
                        Your review
                    </Heading>
                </Flex>
        </Flex>
        
        </>
    )
}
